"title": "8162: spiritual vitality",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8162: spiritual vitality",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The quality of possessing a living faith, which is commended by Scripture.</p>\n<h2>Spiritual vitality commended</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:3\">2TH 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:9\">JOB 17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:7\">PSA 84:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:12\">PSA 92:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:18\">PRO 4:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:15\">1TI 4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:5-2Pet1:7\">2PE 1:5–1:7</a></p>\n<h2>The means of developing spiritual vitality</h2>\n<h3>Abiding in Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:4\">JHN 15:4</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Seeking to imitate Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">EPH 4:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:15\">JHN 13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:14\">ROM 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:1\">1CO 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:27\">GAL 3:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10\">PHP 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21\">1PE 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:6\">1JN 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:28\">1JN 2:28</a></p>\n<h3>Resisting temptation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:14\">1JN 2:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:5\">1CO 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:13\">1CO 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:5\">1TH 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:18\">HEB 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:3\">JAS 1:2–1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:10\">REV 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Developing discipline</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:12\">1TI 6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:7-Heb12:11\">HEB 12:7–12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:18-Rev3:19\">REV 3:18–3:19</a></p>\n<h3>Exhorting others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:2\">1KI 2:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:7\">2CH 15:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:4\">ISA 35:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:4\">HAG 2:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:10\">EPH 6:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:1\">2TI 2:1</a></p>\n<h3>Being filled with the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18\">EPH 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:16-Gal5:18\">GAL 5:16–5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a></p>\n<h2>Obstacles to spiritual vitality</h2>\n<h3>Lack of sound teaching</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:1-2Tim4:3\">2TI 4:1–4:3</a></p>\n<h3>A failure to progress beyond basic teachings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:12\">HEB 5:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:2\">1PE 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of individuals with spiritual vitality</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:26\">1SA 2:26</a> <em>Samuel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:80\">LUK 1:80</a> <em>John the Baptist</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:40\">LUK 2:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:52\">LUK 2:52</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:22\">ACT 9:22</a> <em>Paul</em></p>\n<h2>The consequences of spiritual vitality</h2>\n<h3>Spiritual growth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:18\">2PE 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:11-Eph4:15\">EPH 4:11–4:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:12\">PHP 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">COL 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:7\">1TH 4:3–4:7</a></p>\n<h3>Loving others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:23\">1JN 3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:6\">GAL 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:15\">EPH 1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:23\">EPH 6:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:4-Col1:5\">COL 1:4–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:5\">1TI 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>Rejoicing in the Lord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:4-Phil4:7\">PHP 4:4–4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:11\">PSA 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:5\">PSA 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:21\">PSA 33:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:10\">ISA 35:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:34\">ACT 16:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:12–4:13</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual perseverance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:12\">HEB 6:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:8\">1TH 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:9\">1TI 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:13\">2TI 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:10\">REV 13:10</a></p>",
